sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as kueue-webhook-service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as kueue-controller-manager<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Autoscaler as cluster-autoscaler<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Bearer Token

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission
        User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/batch/v1/jobs<br/>Auth: User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-batch-v1-job<br/>mTLS: API Server client cert
        Webhook->>K8sAPI: Query job details<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Job information
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated job (with queue label)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-batch-v1-job<br/>mTLS: API Server client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
        K8sAPI-->>User: Job created
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Controller,Autoscaler: Flow 2: Workload Reconciliation
        Controller->>K8sAPI: WATCH /apis/batch/v1/jobs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Job event (new job)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/clusterqueues<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: ClusterQueue details
        Controller->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/workloads<br/>Create Workload object
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Workload created

        alt Autoscaling enabled
            Controller->>Autoscaler: POST /apis/autoscaling.x-k8s.io/provisioningrequests<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
            Autoscaler-->>Controller: ProvisioningRequest accepted
        end

        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH /apis/batch/v1/jobs/{name}<br/>Unsuspend job (quota admitted)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Job updated
        Note over Controller: Job pods now created
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(queue depth, admission latency, quotas)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 4: Visibility API Queries
        User->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/visibility.kueue.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/pendingworkloads<br/>Auth: User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Controller: GET visibility-server:8082<br/>mTLS: API Server client cert
        Controller-->>K8sAPI: Pending workloads list
        K8sAPI-->>User: JSON response
    end
